# Git repository safety / Seguridad del repositorio git

This workspace is **only** the Godot plugin `Golem-AI` (`addons/ai_assistant_plugin`).

## Before any git command

1. Run git from the plugin root (where `plugin.cfg` exists).
2. Verify:
   - `git rev-parse --show-toplevel` ends at `ai_assistant_plugin`
   - `git remote get-url origin` contains `Godot-AI-Assistant`
3. If the root is `true-first-person-multiplayer` or another game folder — **STOP**. Wrong repo.

## Never commit from the parent game repo

The parent Godot project has its own git and must ignore this folder (`addons/ai_assistant_plugin/` in parent `.gitignore`).

Do not stage paths like `addons/`, `Maps/`, `Data/`, `project.godot`, or `skills-lock.json` in this plugin repo.

## Commits and pushes

- Commit and push **only** plugin files to `https://github.com/sancheznot/Godot-AI-Assistant.git`
- After `git init` or clone, run `./install_git_hooks.sh` to enable the pre-commit guard
